msgstr "🔑 作为家长，我们的责任就是教会他们保证自身安全，无论他们身在何处。"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "⭐ You are right! "
msgstr "🎈 答对了！ "

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Let’s do a True/False Quiz! My child is always with me, so I don’t need to teach them about safety until they are older."
msgstr "再来一道！判断对错：我会一直在孩子身边保护他们，所以在孩子长大之前，他们没有学习安全知识的必要。"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "💡 It’s important to teach little ones about safety early on, even if they’re always with you. "
msgstr "💡 即使孩子们总是和你在一起，也要尽早对他们进行安全教育。 "

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "🔑 As caregivers, it is our job to help them learn how to stay safe everywhere."
msgstr "🔑 作为家长，我们的责任就是教会他们保证自身安全，无论他们身在何处。"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "⭐ You’re correct! "
msgstr "⭐ 答对了！ "

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "{F3_DAUGHTER_4}: Oh no! My ball!"
msgstr " {F3_DAUGHTER_4} ：啊！我的球到马路上去了！"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "{F3_UNCLE}: Remember what we talked about, {F3_DAUGHTER_4}. What should we do if the ball goes on the street? "
msgstr " {F3_UNCLE} ：你还记得吗， {F3_DAUGHTER_4} ？如果球飞到马路上，我们该怎么办？ "

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "{F3_DAUGHTER_4}: We should stay where we are and ask an adult for help."
msgstr " {F3_DAUGHTER_4} ：我们应该待在原地，找个大人帮忙捡。"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "{F3_UNCLE}: That’s right! I am so proud of you for remembering. Roads are for cars and bikes, and it is safer for an adult to get your ball for you."
msgstr " {F3_UNCLE} ：没错！你还记得，你太棒了。大马路上都是汽车和自行车，大人帮你拿球会更安全。"

#. type=text
#. Strings like @fields.xxx and @results.yyy should not be translated. 
msgctxt "text"
msgid "To keep @fields.child_nickname safe, talk with them about which places are safe to go and which are not, and teach them how to be careful when they meet people they don't know."
msgstr "为了保证 @fields.child_nickname 的安全，请与孩子讨论哪些地方可以去，哪些地方不安全不能去，教他们遇到陌生人时要小心。"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "To keep your child safe, talk with them about which places are safe to go and which are not, and teach them how to be careful when they meet people they don't know."
msgstr "为了保证孩子的安全，请与他们讨论哪些地方可以去，哪些地方不安全不能去，教他们遇到陌生人时要小心。"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Step 1️⃣: DRAW"
msgstr "第1️⃣步：画图"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Step 2️⃣: TALK"
msgstr "第2️⃣步：交谈"

#. type=text
#. Strings like @fields.xxx and @results.yyy should not be translated. 
msgctxt "text"
msgid "🔑 Talk about the safe and unsafe places on your map. For example, let @fields.child_nickname know that the street is not a safe place, even if their toy or ball goes there. "
msgstr "🔑 谈谈地图上哪些地方是安全的，哪些地方是不安全的。例如，让 @fields.child_nickname 知道马路上是不安全的，哪怕玩具或球掉到马路上，他们也不可以过去。 "

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "🔵 CIRCLE the places that are safe for children."
msgstr "🔵 在对孩子来说安全的地方上画个圈。"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "🔑 Talk about the safe and unsafe places on your map. For example, let your child know that the street is not a safe place, even if their toy or ball goes there. "
msgstr "🔑 谈谈地图上哪些地方是安全的，哪些地方是不安全的。例如，让孩子知道马路上是不安全的，哪怕玩具或球掉到马路上，他们也不可以过去。 "

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Step 3️⃣: DISCUSS"
msgstr "第3️⃣步：讨论"

#. type=text
#. Strings like @fields.xxx and @results.yyy should not be translated. 
msgctxt "text"
msgid "❗ Discuss with @fields.child_nickname why it is important to ALWAYS have an adult with them when they go outside. "
msgstr "❗ 和 @fields.child_nickname 讨论，为什么他们出门时❗ 一定❗ 要有大人陪着。 "

#. type=text
#. Strings like @fields.xxx and @results.yyy should not be translated. 
msgctxt "text"
msgid "👀 Discuss with @fields.child_nickname safe places they can run if a stranger approaches them – such as your home, or a neighbour’s home. "
msgstr "👀 和 @fields.child_nickname 讨论，如果有陌生人靠近，他们可以跑去哪些安全的地方，比如自己家或者邻居家。 "

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "🚩 Mark these areas clearly on your map."
msgstr "🚩 在地图上，把这些地方标清楚。"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "❗ Discuss with your child why it is important to ALWAYS have an adult with them when they go outside. "
msgstr "❗ 和孩子讨论，为什么他们出门时❗ 一定❗ 要有大人陪着。 "

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "👀 Discuss with your child safe places they can run if a stranger approaches them – such as your home, or a neighbour’s home. "
msgstr "👀 和孩子讨论，如果有陌生人靠近，他们可以跑去哪些安全的地方，比如自己家或者邻居家。 "

#. type=text
#. Strings like @fields.xxx and @results.yyy should not be translated. 
msgctxt "text"
msgid "⭐ Praise when @fields.child_nickname chooses the correct response, such as running away, shouting for help, or finding a trusted adult."
msgstr "⭐ 如果 @fields.child_nickname 选择了正确的应对方式——如逃跑、大声呼救或寻找可信赖的大人，请一定要给予表扬。"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "⭐ Praise when your child chooses the correct response, such as running away, shouting for help, or finding a trusted adult."
msgstr "⭐ 如果孩子选择了正确的应对方式——如逃跑、大声呼救或寻找可信赖的大人，请一定要给予表扬。"

#. type=text
#. Strings like @fields.xxx and @results.yyy should not be translated. 
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Talking about unsafe situations with @fields.child_nickname might feel uncomfortable, but it's important. When children know what to do in a dangerous situation, they're much safer."
msgstr "和 @fields.child_nickname 谈论不安全的情况，这可能会让你感到不习惯、不适应，但这很重要。只有孩子们知道在危险的情况下该怎么做，才可能保障他们的安全。"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Talking about unsafe situations with your child might feel uncomfortable, but it's important. When children know what to do in a dangerous situation, they're much safer."
msgstr "和孩子谈论不安全的情况，这可能会让你感到不习惯、不适应，但这很重要。只有孩子们知道在危险的情况下该怎么做，才可能保障他们的安全。"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Home activity! ⭐"
msgstr "家庭练习！⭐ "

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Do you have time to do it today? ⏰"
msgstr "你今天有时间试一试吗？⏰"

#. type=text
#. Strings like @fields.xxx and @results.yyy should not be translated. 
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Great! 💙 You are helping @fields.child_nickname be aware of their surroundings to keep themselves safe."
msgstr "太棒了！💙 这样，你就能帮@fields.child_nickname 了解了周围环境，从而保证孩子的日常安全。"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Great! 💙 You are helping your child be aware of their surroundings to keep themselves safe."
msgstr "太棒了！💙  这样，你就能帮孩子了解了周围环境，从而保证他们的日常安全。"

#. type=text
#. Strings like @fields.xxx and @results.yyy should not be translated. 
msgctxt "text"
msgid "That's OK! If you don't have time today, set some time aside tomorrow to talk to @fields.child_nickname about safe and unsafe places. You can do this! 🌷"
msgstr "没关系！如果你今天没有时间，试着明天抽点时间，来和 @fields.child_nickname 谈谈安全和不安全的地方。你可以做到的！🌷"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "That's OK! If you don't have time today, set some time aside tomorrow to talk to your child about safe and unsafe places. You can do this! 🌷"
msgstr "没关系。如果你今天没时间，那么试着明天抽点时间，来和孩子讨论一下日常安全问题吧。加油，你可以的！🌷"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "😔 Your child could experience harm in any of these places, even at home or at school. "
msgstr "😔 孩子可能在任何地方受到伤害，哪怕是在家里或学校。 "

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Let’s check in on {F3_SON_7} and his mother, {F3_MOTHER} after {F3_SON_7} finds himself in an uncomfortable situation:"
msgstr "让我们来看看，当{F3_SON_7}遇到危险时，{F3_SON_7}和他的母亲{F3_MOTHER}是怎么做的："

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "{F3_MOTHER}: What is it, {F3_SON_7}!? Take a breath and tell me."
msgstr " {F3_MOTHER} ：什么事， {F3_SON_7} ？ 先深呼吸一下，然后告诉我。"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "{F3_SON_7}: My name is {F3_SON_7}."
msgstr " {F3_SON_7} ：我叫 {F3_SON_7} 。"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "{MAN_IN_CAR}: {F3_SON_7}, such a beautiful name."
msgstr " {MAN_IN_CAR} ： {F3_SON_7} ，名字真好听。"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "{F3_SON_7}: Thank you."
msgstr " {F3_SON_7} ：谢谢。"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "{F3_SON_7}: No, thank you."
msgstr " {F3_SON_7} ：不用，谢谢。"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "{F3_SON_7}: Mummyyyyyy!!"
msgstr " {F3_SON_7} ：妈妈妈妈！！！"

#. type=text
#. Strings like @fields.xxx and @results.yyy should not be translated. 
msgctxt "text"
msgid "🚩 Include the main places: streets, your house, school, shops, and places @fields.child_nickname visits."
msgstr "🚩 包括主要地点：街道、你的住处、学校、商店和 @fields.child_nickname 经常去的地方。"

#. type=text
#. Strings like @fields.xxx and @results.yyy should not be translated. 
msgctxt "text"
msgid "👋Draw and identify pictures of trusted people who @fields.child_nickname can go to when they feel unsafe. These can be you and your spouse, other family members, or teachers."
msgstr "👋 画出 @fields.child_nickname 可以信任的人，当孩子感到不安全时，可以去找这些人。这些人可以是你、你的爱人、其他家庭成员或老师。"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "🚩 Include the main places: streets, your house, school, shops, and places your child visits."
msgstr "🚩 包括主要地点：街道、你的住处、学校、商店和你的孩子经常去的地方。"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "👋Draw and identify pictures of trusted people who your child can go to when they feel unsafe. These can be you and your spouse, other family members, or teachers."
msgstr "👋 画出孩子可以信任的人，当孩子感到不安全时，可以去找这些人。这些人可以是你、你的爱人、其他家庭成员或老师。"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "🔑 Talk about the places on your map and decide if they are safe or not."
msgstr "🔑 讨论地图上的地点，并确定它们是否安全。"

#. type=text
#. Strings like @fields.xxx and @results.yyy should not be translated. 
msgctxt "text"
msgid "👂 Listen to @fields.child_nickname: it is important to understand why they think a place is safe or unsafe."
msgstr "👂 听听 @fields.child_nickname 的想法，了解他们为什么认为某个地方安全或不安全，这非常重要。"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "👂 Listen to your child: it is important to understand why they think a place is safe or unsafe."
msgstr "👂 听听孩子的想法，了解他们为什么认为某个地方安全或不安全，这非常重要。"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "❗ Sometimes, we find ourselves in trouble."
msgstr "❗ 有时候，我们会遇到麻烦。"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "✨ Give space for your child to share their thoughts, too. They may think a place is unsafe that you thought was safe. Allow them to explain their reasons. Do you have time to do it today? ⏰"
msgstr ""
"✨ 给孩子留点空间，让他们也能分享自己的想法。\n"
"你可能觉得某个地方很安全，但孩子却不这么认为。这时，要让他们解释感到不安全的理由。\n"
"\n"
"你今天有时间试一试吗？⏰"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "When our children share something that is very hard or upsetting to them😔😣, we need to remember to stay calm, listen, and be open, so that they feel supported. 💛"
msgstr "当孩子跟我们分享一些让他们感到非常害怕或者难过的事情时😔😣，我们要始终记得保持冷静、耐心和开放包容，让他们感受到爱与支持。💛"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "True or False: When my child is upset, I should wait for them to come to me. I don’t want to upset them further by asking what is troubling them."
msgstr "判断对错：当我的孩子遇到困难、感到烦闷时，我应该等他们主动来找我。我不想主动去问他们遇到了什么麻烦，因为这会让他们更加不安。"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "❌ Incorrect."
msgstr "❌ 不对哦。"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "💚 You can ask your child very calmly about why they seem upset. 👀"
msgstr "💚 你可以问问孩子，为什么最近总是看起来心烦意乱。在询问的过程中，记得要始终保持冷静。👀"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "👂 Assure them that you are proud of how brave they are to share their crisis with you."
msgstr "👂 让他们知道，主动诉说自己的困难是一种勇敢的表现，你为他们感到骄傲。"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "🌷 That’s right!"
msgstr "🌷 答对了！"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "{F1_SON_5} looks upset. Let’s see how his father, {F1_FATHER} responds:"
msgstr "{F1_SON_5}看起来心烦意乱。让我们看看，他的爸爸{F1_FATHER}是如何应对的："

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "{F1_SON_5} (crying): He and some of the other kids were mean to me. They said I was stupid because I can’t button my shirt properly."
msgstr " {F1_SON_5} （哭着说）：他和其他几个人对我很坏，因为我扣不上衬衫他们就说我笨。"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "{F1_SON_5}: Okay…"
msgstr " {F1_SON_5} ：想..."

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Thank you for sharing with me, {F1_SON_5}. I am very proud of you."
msgstr "谢谢你能和我分享， {F1_SON_5} 。 我真为你骄傲。"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "▶️ Press play to learn the 4️⃣ four things you can do to support your child when they share something difficult with you."
msgstr "▶️ 点击“播放”，开始学习4️⃣种帮孩子学会应对危机的小方法吧。"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "4️⃣ Here are four things you can do to support your child when they share something difficult with you:"
msgstr "当孩子和你诉说他们遇到的危机时，你可以做以下4️⃣件事来给予支持："

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "1️⃣ BREATHE: Take a pause"
msgstr "1️⃣ 深呼吸：暂停一下。"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "🌱 Take a deep breath so you can respond calmly."
msgstr "🌱 深呼吸，然后心平气和地回应。"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "💛 Ask yourself, “What does my child need right now?”"
msgstr "💛 问问你自己：“我的孩子现在最需要什么？”"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "2️⃣ LISTEN: Ask your child what is going on "
msgstr "2️⃣ 倾听：问问孩子发生了什么事"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "👀 Notice what they are feeling and tell them what you notice so they feel heard. "
msgstr "👀关注孩子的感受。告诉他们你理解他们的感受，让他们意识到自己是被关爱的。"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "💙 Tell your child that you are there for them and love them."
msgstr "💙告诉孩子，你会一直在他们身边。"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "😣Both girls AND boys could face hard times and crisis situations. Remember to check-in with both."
msgstr "😣无论男孩还是女孩，都可能面临困难和危机，都需要你的关注和支持。"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "➡️ You might need to talk about the actions that you or your child could take to help with what has happened."
msgstr "➡️ 接着，可能需要讨论你们可以采取哪些行动，来帮助解决问题。"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "✅ Remember, you can always type {HELP} to ParentText and get information about resources in your community where you can receive help."
msgstr "✅ 别忘了，你可以随时输入 {HELP} 来获取相关资源，以便获得支持。"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "4️⃣ COMFORT: Be there for your child"
msgstr "4️⃣ 安慰：陪伴孩子"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "🌷 It can be hard to see your child feeling upset or confused, but there is a lot you can do to support them."
msgstr "🌷看到孩子不安或迷茫，可能会让你很难受，但你能提供的帮助有很多。"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "💚 They need you to accept them and comfort them when difficult things are going on."
msgstr "💚在遇到困难时，他们需要你的接纳和安慰。"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "🔄In these moments, maintaining a consistent routine can be particularly helpful. Familiar routines can provide a sense of security and normalcy, helping your child feel safe again."
msgstr "🔄在这种情况下，更需要让孩子保持规律作息。熟悉的作息安排能让孩子感到安全，尽快恢复日常生活，消除他们的不安情绪。"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "🎈 Remind your child again that you love them, and thank them for sharing with you."
msgstr "🎈再次提醒孩子你爱他们，谢谢他们能与你诉说自己遇到的困难。"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Home Activity! ⭐ "
msgstr "家庭练习！⭐"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Do you have time to do this today? ⏰"
msgstr "你今天有时间试一试吗？⏰"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "{F2_GRANDMOTHER}: My dear, you look really upset, do you want to tell me what happened?"
msgstr " {F2_GRANDMOTHER} ：宝贝，你看起来很不开心，你想和我聊聊发生了什么吗？"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "{F2_DAUGHTER_8}: It’s true, he… he… made me very uncomfortable… he touched my body and told me I’d be in trouble if I told anybody! I didn’t want to do anything with him, and I even said NO, but he told me I would be in trouble."
msgstr " {F2_DAUGHTER_8} ：是真的，他...他...让我很不舒服，我不想让他摸我，也明确和他说了”不行“，但他还是威胁我，说如果我告诉别人，我就会有麻烦！"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "{F2_GRANDMOTHER}: You are so brave for sharing this with me. You are not in trouble. This is not your fault. Thank you for telling me."
msgstr " {F2_GRANDMOTHER} ：你能和我讲这件事，真的很勇敢！有妈妈在，你不会遇到麻烦的，这也不是你的错。谢谢你愿意告诉我。"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "{F2_DAUGHTER_8}: Yesterday, when you went to see your friend, he just came here and that’s when it happened."
msgstr " {F2_DAUGHTER_8} ：昨天你去见朋友的时候，他来了。就是那个时候。"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "{F2_DAUGHTER_8}: Yes… Okay… where will we go?"
msgstr " {F2_DAUGHTER_8} ：好的...我们去哪呀？"

#. type=text
#. Strings like @fields.xxx and @results.yyy should not be translated. 
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Amazing! 💙This can help prepare you and @fields.child_nickname to face hard situations AND avoid them in the first place."
msgstr "太棒了！💙这能帮助你和 @fields.child_nickname 更好地避免陷入困境，应对危机。"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Amazing! 💙This can help prepare you and your child to face hard situations AND avoid them in the first place."
msgstr ""
"太棒了！💙这能帮助你和孩子免于陷入困境。\n"
"\n"
"而且就算危机真的发生了，你和孩子也能有所准备、更好地应对它。"

#. type=text
#. Strings like @fields.xxx and @results.yyy should not be translated. 
msgctxt "text"
msgid "That's OK! Plan to set aside an hour in the next few days to have this chat with @fields.child_nickname. This can help prepare you and @fields.child_nickname to face hard situations AND avoid them in the first place."
msgstr "没关系！在接下来的几天里留出一个小时和 @fields.child_nickname 聊聊。这有助于你和 @fields.child_nickname 更好地避免陷入困境，应对危机。"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "That's OK! Plan to set aside an hour in the next few days to have this chat with your child. This can help prepare you and your child to face hard situations AND avoid them in the first place."
